fields.title: CEO and Co-Founder
fields.bio: Irina is a Co-Founder and CEO of 4Schoolers. As a mother and a teacher with a background in education, she always struggled to balance guaranteeing a quality education to her kids with her own work. This led her to found 4Schoolers to help other parents guarantee a quality and specifically tailored education experience.

fields.title: Lead Engineer
fields.education: B.S. in Mathematics and Computer Science
fields.bio: Talented Mathematician and Computer Scientist with solid experience in Quantitative Development, Algorithmic Trading, Mathematical Modeling, and Web Development. Launched various open-sourced web applications with a couple of thousands of active users from the USA, Russia, India, Vietnam, and other countries.
